videos.headline: Illinois runs play-action pass to perfection
videos.description: Illinois QB Brandon Peters fakes the handoff and throws to a wide-open Donny Navarro for a 31-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Illinois runs play-action pass to perfection) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Iowa QB avoids sack, completes 40-yard pass
videos.description: Iowa QB Nate Stanley spins out of a sack and throws off his back foot to WR Ihmir Smith-Marsette who snags it for a 40-yard completion.
